utils.fhir

Class PersonResourceProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • utils.fhir.ResourceProvider<org.hl7.fhir.dstu3.model.Person>
      • utils.fhir.PersonResourceProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ca.uhn.fhir.rest.server.IResourceProvider

    public class PersonResourceProvider
extends ResourceProvider<org.hl7.fhir.dstu3.model.Person>
implements ca.uhn.fhir.rest.server.IResourceProvider
    FHIR resource provider for the "Person" resource. Unlike other resources this resource type triggers a user search on the account database. Creates, updates and deletes are not allowed.
